-They've no patience.

163
00:08:44.520 --> 00:08:46.256
She moves around the town like that.

164
00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:49.176
That's bob on. They call her
Miss Pru Never Queue.

165
00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:51.216
Yeah. she lives alone.

166
