Here. let's get
these product placed.

208
00:11:00.880 --> 00:11:03.496
Ooh! 25% off.

209
00:11:03.520 --> 00:11:05.936
-Get this. Dobbie.
-Oh. I'll have some of that.

210
00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:07.416
